item.title: Swati Vishwanath Shirke
item.description: My name is Swati Vishwanath Shirke. I am pursuing a masters in robotics engineering. My areas of interest are in Robot Control and Motion Planning. Currently I am working on aerial transportation using multiple quadrotor drones under Professor Guanrui Li. In the past I worked on builidng a control system for mobile robots, autonomous vehicles and manupilators. I have also built motion planning algorithms for mobile robots and autonomous vehicles.
